FEMALE SPEAKER: Thanks
everyone for coming.

00:00:04.310 --> 00:00:08.070
I'm just going to introduce
Ruth here.

00:00:08.070 --> 00:00:11.550
I've personally been connected
with AJWS, the American Jewish

00:00:11.550 --> 00:00:15.180
World Service, for a
number of years.

00:00:15.180 --> 00:00:17.930
I did a volunteer trip in El
Salvador with them many years

00:00:17.930 --> 00:00:21.490
ago, helping post-earthquake
relief reconstruction.

00:00:21.490 --> 00:00:26.930
That's one of the many, many
projects that AJWS organizes.

00:00:26.930 --> 00:00:30.510
And so I was thrilled when I was
contacted by AJWS telling

00:00:30.510 --> 00:00:34.140
me that Ruth wanted to come and
speak with us about many

00:00:34.140 --> 00:00:36.600
