We will increasingly going
forward, strategically as a

00:47:34.430 --> 00:47:38.660
lesson we've learned over the
last 15 years, we will target

00:47:38.660 --> 00:47:39.910
our disaster--

00:47:42.030 --> 00:47:45.830
our visibility after a disaster
will be targeted to

00:47:45.830 --> 00:47:48.500
the extent that it's a country
in which we already work.

00:47:48.500 --> 00:47:51.670
That doesn't mean we'll refuse,
because disasters

00:47:51.670 --> 00:47:55.860
because of media and because
of sad stories and drama,

00:47:55.860 --> 00:47:58.750
disasters are one of the few
issues that get covered in the

00:47:58.750 --> 00:47:59.440
American press.

00:47:59.440 --> 00:48:02.420
And so it's one of the times for
us to capture new donors.

00:48:02.420 --> 00:48:04.775
So God forbid if there was a
disaster tomorrow in a country

00:48:04.775 --> 00:48:07.780
in which we've never worked, we
would put ourselves on the

00:48:07.780 --> 00:48:10.280
Google lists, on "The New
York Times" list.

00:48:10.280 --> 00:48:13.700
But we would also strategize
within 36 hours, because

00:48:13.700 --> 00:48:16.130
that's about the window that we
have, as to, OK, if we get

00:48:16.130 --> 00:48:18.460
a lot of money for this
disaster, exactly what are we

00:48:18.460 --> 00:48:20.470
going to do, because it's
not a country in

00:48:20.470 --> 00:48:21.660
which we've done work?

00:48:21.660 --> 00:48:24.580
And the most likely answer is we
partner with some people or

00:48:24.580 --> 00:48:29.320
we tell people, if you want to
feed people tomorrow, actually

00:48:29.320 --> 00:48:30.590
don't send the money to us.

00:48:30.590 --> 00:48:33.260
Because it's going to take us
two months to figure out.

00:48:33.260 --> 00:48:34.200
That's on the first hand.

00:48:34.200 --> 00:48:37.290
On the other hand, countries
where we have worked, where we

00:48:37.290 --> 00:48:40.350
know grassroots groups, I'm
just going to say right up

00:48:40.350 --> 00:48:42.780
front, we are infinitely better
placed to do your

00:48:42.780 --> 00:48:46.300
relief money, because the money
will actually get to the

00:48:46.300 --> 00:48:48.500
people in need almost
immediately.

00:48:48.500 --> 00:48:51.860
And it won't all be spent at
once, because in Haiti the

00:48:51.860 --> 00:48:56.570
story is not just what did
people need right away.

00:48:56.570 --> 00:49:00.050
Haiti's a country that fed its
entire population on its own,

00:49:00.050 --> 00:49:02.300
off of its own land
50 years ago.

00:49:02.300 --> 00:49:06.640
And it's now totally dependent
on expensive imports.

00:49:06.640 --> 00:49:09.190
And the big danger after
something like the earthquake

00:49:09.190 --> 00:49:12.290
is that it will only
make that worse.

00:49:12.290 --> 00:49:15.900
The more food aid we bring in,
the lower the options for

00:49:15.900 --> 00:49:16.900
Haitian farmers.

00:49:16.900 --> 00:49:18.820
And so we're really
pretty smart.

00:49:18.820 --> 00:49:22.200
We received $6.5 million
after the earthquake.

00:49:22.200 --> 00:49:25.720
And we didn't tell every $10
donor, but we told every

00:49:25.720 --> 00:49:30.080
decent sized donor, this is a
five year plan for investment

00:49:30.080 --> 00:49:33.710
in protecting women and
girls and agricultural

00:49:33.710 --> 00:49:35.470
sustainability in Haiti.

00:49:35.470 --> 00:49:37.300
And if you want to spend it
tomorrow, give it to someone

00:49:37.300 --> 00:49:38.940
else, but it won't
be as useful.

00:49:38.940 --> 00:49:44.190
We had eight project partner
organizations in Haiti at the

00:49:44.190 --> 00:49:47.870
time of the earthquake, two that
we had funded previously.

00:49:47.870 --> 00:49:51.930
We now have 41, because they
lead us to others.

00:49:51.930 --> 00:49:55.760
[APPLAUSE]

00:49:55.760 --> 00:49:58.190
RUTH MESSINGER: Oh, I forgot
to say first of all that we

00:49:58.190 --> 00:50:01.980
advertise our trips on our
website, which is ajws.org.

00:50:01.980 --> 00:50:05.530
And second of all, despite my
evident advanced age, I want

00:50:05.530 --> 00:50:06.780
you all to know that I tweet.

